      "text": "Revelations : The Demon Slayer (女神転生外伝 ラストバイブル) is a role-playing video game developed by  Access and Multimedia Intelligence Transfer, and published by Atlus, Index and Sega, initially released on Game Boy on December 25, 1992 in Japan under the name ‘'Megami Tensei Gaiden: Last Bible’'. It is the first color RPG for Game Boy Color released in North America.",
